project.title: Digital Libraries - Latino USA Arts & Culture
project.description: This project was made for the Digital Libraries Presentation Project at UT Austin in October 2025. Using a collection of Latino USA program recordings we highlight the variety of arts and culture topics covered across the episodes.
project.creator: luzgonz-glitch
project.authors: Luz Gonzalez, Allysa Tellez, Christian Nicholas, Katie Galyon
